  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether Cloderm Cream is effective for topical
      treatment of moderate psoriasis over 28 days.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to estimate the efficacy of Cloderm Cream for topical
      treatment of moderate plaque psoriasis over 28 days using current standards for evaluation.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
